We're back for another Zig Day hosted by [Parallel Wireless](https://www.parallelwireless.com/) in
Bristol! See [the Bristol page](/europe/bristol) for the format.

## RSVP

Like last time, if you're planning to attend, **you must [RSVP using Luma][luma]**. On the day,
someone will be by the building entrance from 10:00 to check your tickets and let you in. If you
arrive a bit later or get locked out, call 07599918784 and someone will come down to let you in.

[luma]: https://luma.com/k9n5lz69
